  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized </p><p>When you hit a creature you may spend 1 superiority die.</p><p> When you do so, you may shoot your grapple hook at another creature, structure, or object within 60 feet and pull you towards it without expending your movement.</p><p> If it would put you within 5 feet of a hostile creature when you end your movement you may make an attack with each your Blades of Retribution.</p><p> This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p><p></p>",
